metadata.name: BUFFALO BATH-1
metadata.description:
Buffaloes that pasturing all day on the mountain foot of Erciyes in Kayseri have a bath in the wetland on the way back. The end of day bath of buffaloes displays visual feast to us. Don't pass unless you view these series!

Location : Kayseri / Turkey

Date : 29.07.2021

Dimensions :6480*4320 300 dpi

Edition : 1/1
